com.orientechnologies.orient.stresstest

Class OStressTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.stresstest.OStressTester

  • public class OStressTester
extends Object
    The main class of the OStressTester. It is instantiated from the OStressTesterCommandLineParser and takes care of launching the needed threads (OOperationsExecutor) for executing the operations of the test.
    Author:
    Andrea Iacono
